Let's get this grand final going.
让我们正式开始这场总决赛。

3
00:00:10,266 --> 00:00:12,366
We've got Na'Vi and Vitality.
对阵双方是 Na'Vi 和 Vitality。

4
00:00:12,366 --> 00:00:13,833
It's a rematch.
这是一场复仇战。

5
00:00:14,066 --> 00:00:16,033
And Na'Vi are back for blood.
而 Na'Vi 这次就是来复仇的。

6
00:00:17,966 --> 00:00:20,700
the first test is for makazze, brought up on the desk,
第一个考验来到了makazze 

7
00:00:20,700 --> 00:00:22,066
he has to pass this.
他必须得先过这一关。

8
00:00:22,566 --> 00:00:24,733
Guarding outside, going one for one,
外场防守先打成一换一，

9
00:00:25,233 --> 00:00:26,033
might be enough.
这也许已经够了。

10
00:00:26,033 --> 00:00:29,266
Plenty of information, but instantly flameZ appears.
信息已经拿满了，但 flameZ 瞬间现身。

11
00:00:34,966 --> 00:00:36,866
Bit of a reset on the situation.
局势稍微缓了一下。

12
00:00:38,633 --> 00:00:40,333
They now can't see the cross, and flameZ,
现在他们已经看不到过点了，而 flameZ

13
00:00:40,333 --> 00:00:42,733
