还在外场故意制造动静。

14
00:00:43,166 --> 00:00:44,733
iM walks into this, but he's fine.
iM 直接走进来了，但他处理得很稳。

15
00:00:44,833 --> 00:00:45,666
So clean.
太干净了。

16
00:00:47,233 --> 00:00:50,466
So clean, clinical triple tap out of that one.
太干净了，这波冷静利落地连收三人。

17
00:00:50,466 --> 00:00:52,433
flameZ, what recovery can you make?
flameZ，你还能怎么补救？

18
00:00:52,566 --> 00:00:54,566
I bet absolutely nothing.
我看基本没戏了。

19
00:00:54,566 --> 00:00:55,500
Minute on the clock.
时间还剩一分钟。

20
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:57,500
Bomb on the opposite side of the map here, Mohan.
炸弹可还在地图另一头呢，Mohan。

21
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:58,533
That is the kind
这就是那种

22
00:00:58,533 --> 00:00:59,900
of clinical precision
极度冷静、极度精准的处理，

23
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:01,466
that we're gonna need from somebody out of Na'Vi
今晚 Na'Vi 必须得有人打出这种表现

24
00:01:01,466 --> 00:01:02,100
at the get-go.
从开局就得站出来。

25
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:04,133
Like Mauisnake said, even when it's B1ad3, maybe,
就像 Mauisnake 说的，哪怕是 B1ad3 也好，

26
00:01:04,166 --> 00:01:05,533
taking timeouts a little too late,
有时候暂停都叫得稍微晚了一点，

27
00:01:05,533 --> 00:01:06,433
whatever it needs to be,
不管问题到底出在哪，

28
00:01:06,433 --> 00:01:08,533
it's gotta start well for Na'Vi tonight.
今晚 Na'Vi 都必须先把开局打好。

29
00:01:09,066 --> 00:01:12,233
Yep, I was looking back at this core. Oh, okay.
对，我刚刚还在回看这套核心数据。哦，等等。

30
00:01:12,466 --> 00:01:14,733
Wait a second, he's got that second headshot,
等一下，他连第二个爆头都拿到了，

31
00:01:14,733 --> 00:01:16,066
meant to be impossible.
这本来几乎是不可能的。

32
00:01:16,166 --> 00:01:18,033
Two players on top of that bomb had possession.
当时可是有两个人已经踩住了包点位置。

33
00:01:18,033 --> 00:01:19,366
He catches them in transition.
结果他正好抓到对手转移的瞬间。

34
00:01:19,366 --> 00:01:21,833
He teases them with the feet on the ladder.
他在梯子上露脚，故意把对面钓出来。

35
00:01:22,033 --> 00:01:23,233
This is interesting, actually.
这下其实有点意思了。

36
00:01:23,233 --> 00:01:25,066
Aleksib's got a smoke to work with.
Aleksib 手里还有一颗烟。

37
00:01:25,066 --> 00:01:26,100
flameZ has 11 HP.
flameZ 只剩 11 点血。

38
00:01:26,100 --> 00:01:27,733
But we're talking about pistol round.
但别忘了，这可是手枪局。

39
00:01:28,833 --> 00:01:30,266
P250 comes out.
P250 掏出来了。

40
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:32,666
One headshot makes the difference. Let's see.
只要一个爆头就能改写结局，看看吧。

41
00:01:36,033 --> 00:01:37,333
Wow, that was close.
哇，这也太接近了。

42
00:01:38,433 --> 00:01:40,900
Very nice round out of b1t, obviously.
这回合 b1t 打得确实漂亮。

